    "description": "该模板是GameCreator官方出品的游戏模板-《苍之羽》。<br>是一款无任何自带战斗系统的RPG游戏模板，可用于制作剧情、解谜等游戏。<br>同时也利于高级开发人员扩展追加战斗系统。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >请注意：该DLC内容已包含在软件本体内，该页面仅供展示该模板包含的部分内容</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/c8c779de9242ace0447a9d4b039ecea9.avif?t=1742051181\" width=620 height=349 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏手柄和SteamDeck支持</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/4bb444fd73c06756a125e9a7ffe91d3a.avif?t=1742051181\" width=620 height=272 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可视化编辑</h2>支持全程使用可视化编辑游戏内容。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/b98229545a0bc2632eff080b9d9ceced.poster.avif?t=1742051181\" width=620 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/b98229545a0bc2632eff080b9d9ceced.webm?t=1742051181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/b98229545a0bc2632eff080b9d9ceced.mp4?t=1742051181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特性</h2>支持1~8方向的行走图<br>支持走格子移动以及像素级移动<br>支持按键跑步（可设置跑步动作）<br>支持存档与读档，自行添加的属性会自动进入存档<br>支持自定义设置网格大小（默认48）、分辨率<br>支持绘制图块和自动元件<br>支持整张图片作为地图图层，支持多层远景<br>拥有背包道具和商店系统<br>默认支持游戏手柄、键盘、鼠标操作<br>支持超多事件<br>可视化设置行走图、动画、立绘、界面等<br>支持脚本扩展（TypeScript）和插件<br>更多特性，期待您的体验！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于模板内置的素材</h2>模板内置了大量像素风的素材以及音乐、音效、界面等等。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/040ec3ad5c52cea5334d54a28473f476.poster.avif?t=1742051181\" width=620 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/040ec3ad5c52cea5334d54a28473f476.webm?t=1742051181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/040ec3ad5c52cea5334d54a28473f476.mp4?t=1742051181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/cd9ac3361243ab44ccf584fdab9e4c21.poster.avif?t=1742051181\" width=620 height=530 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/cd9ac3361243ab44ccf584fdab9e4c21.webm?t=1742051181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/cd9ac3361243ab44ccf584fdab9e4c21.mp4?t=1742051181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/f09cf3e16d747153e6d2041cd18be2ed.poster.avif?t=1742051181\" width=620 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/f09cf3e16d747153e6d2041cd18be2ed.webm?t=1742051181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/f09cf3e16d747153e6d2041cd18be2ed.mp4?t=1742051181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/21fc4fb52113e0323a9fe6daaf532127.avif?t=1742051181\" width=620 height=474 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196710/extras/9ecf36e388334a0d5112bdcc69e20653.avif?t=1742051181\" width=620 height=212 /></span><br><span